com.vmware.appliance.networking.interfaces

Interface Ipv6

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Ipv6Types, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ipv6Stub

    public interface Ipv6
extends Service, Ipv6Types
    The Ipv6 interface provides methods to perform IPv6 network configuration for interfaces. This interface was added in vSphere API 6.7.
